    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this research study is to compare the efficacy
      (reduction in HbA1c and in blood glucose levels) of insulin detemir once daily injection
      compared to insulin detemir twice daily injection administered as basal insulin for the
      treatment of type 1 diabetes and to verify the safety of use (number and severity of episodes
      of hypoglycemia, body weight and side effects).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
